room_title: Escape room "The Egyptian Tomb Escape" by Master Escape Room in Miami
room_address: 1700 North Dixie Hwy, Boca Raton, FL 33432
room_description: Your archaeological team is on a quest of the ancient pyramids. As the group descends deeper and deeper, you stop to take a picture and lose sight of them. Somehow you end up in a room with a coffin and activate a trap, leaving you locked with a mummy. Suddenly it starts to move... Can you find a way out of here before you have to meet face to face with a dead pharaoh?
